        },
        {
            "_id": "F58s1zGhxWZhyyU7",
            "data": {
                "actionCategory": {
                    "value": "offensive"
                },
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Anitoli Nostreaema siphons the breath from living creatures, sapping their strength. A living creature hit by a jaws Strike must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:24] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 24 hours and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fatigued]{Fatigued}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is enfeebled 1 for 24 hours, is fatigued, and falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious}.</p>"
                },
